  "method": [
    "Cook meat, garlic, and onion in a frying pan over medium heat for ten",
    "minutes or until beef is no redder and veggies are soft, splitting meat",
    "into crumbles; clean.",
    "Insert the oregano and half a teaspoon of salt.",
    "Mix the yogurt, onion, cucumber, dill, and the leftover salt in a",
    "shallow dish.",
    "Pour the mixture over each pita bread with ¾ cup meat combination;",
    "finish with two tablespoons of yogurt sauce.",
    "Cover with optional tomatoes and cucumbers if needed. With the",
    "leftover yogurt sauce, eat."
  ],
